1️⃣ 110m hurdles
2️⃣ a 3000m steeplechase
3️⃣ high jump
4️⃣ long jump
5️⃣ a 100m sprint 
... aka a pentathlon *ON A BIKE*!? 🤯

Tomomi has just given us the trials biking/athletics crossover we had *no idea* we needed so head over to ~link in bio~ to watch the mastery in full 📺
